Hi there, welcome to my password manager application. I have created and built this password manager which will store your passwords in a database so you can always add, update or remove passwords at your discretion. This application was made in Visual Studios 2017 and using the C# programming language to create it.
In this password manager you will find a few ways of managing your passwords, such as:-
1. SHOW PASSWORDS - Shows all passwords saved in the database. 2. ADD NEW PASSWORD - Adds a new password to the database. 3. UPDATE/DELETE PASSWORD - Update or delete passwords in the database. 4. PRINT PASSWORDS - Print all passwords shown in the dashboard. 5. ABOUT - Just a brief history of why and how to use this application. 6. GUIDELINES - shows how to make a good strong password to stop hackers.
Please create an account so you are registered to use this application, then you can save, update or delete passwords at your own will.
Thank you and I hope you enjoy this project of mine.
Jonathan Atkinson 07/04/2019
